# Title: Sysmon Driver Unloaded Via Fltmc.EXE
# Author: Kirill Kiryanov, oscd.community
# Date: 2019-10-23
# Level: high
# Description: Detects possible Sysmon filter driver unloaded via fltmc.exe
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1070, attack.t1685, attack.t1685.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_fltmc_unload_driver_sysmon.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

CommandLine="*unload*" CommandLine="*sysmon*" Image="*\\fltMC.exe" OR OriginalFileName="fltMC.exe"